title: PML-N’s Ahsan Iqbal Chaudhary wins NA-76 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz’ (PML-N) Candidate Ahsan Iqbal Chaudhary has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-76 Narowal-II by securing 1,36,279 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Javed Safdar Kahloon, who bagged 109,309 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 50.27 percent.
